SURVEY OF CHILDREN'S SERVICES IN OHIO PUBLIC LIBRARIES 1979.SURVEY CARRIED OUT BY THE OHIO LIBRARY ASSOCIATION SERVICE TO CHILDREN ANDYOUNG TEENS DIVISION. QUESTIONNAIRES WERE SENT TO LIBRARIES WITH NO LISTEDBRANCHES, CHILDREN'S SERVICE COORDINATORS, BRANCH LIBRARIES, AND PUBLICLIBRARIES OFFERING A BOOKMOBILE SERVICE. RESULTS WERE ANALYSED AND SUMMARISEDUNDER 5 HEADINGS: CHILDREN'S SERVICES AND ADMINISTRATION; STAFF; MATERIALS;PROGRAMMES AND PRACTICES; AND SERVICES BEYOND THE LIBRARY